      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "2. This is a mere fiction, which, being confidently affirmed, they thought would easily find belief with a king whose heart and ears they possessed by their hired counsellors, and others of their friends, or the enemies of the Jews. ",
        "children": []
