        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " generally expressed; i.e. from exile on the banks of the Euphrates to dwell in Judæa and Jerusalem. The introductory statement of the subject.",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "p",
