        "text": "they are building.",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " A separate clause, containing an epitome of the charge against the Jews. ‘The rebellious and the bad city’, cf. ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "Ezra 4:15",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ". An appeal to its antecedents was calculated to prejudice the king against Jerusalem.",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "p",
        "text": "",
        "children": [
